      "risk": "Duplicate notifications sent to customers due to at-least-once delivery",
      "severity": "high",
      "mitigation": "Implement idempotency in each Channel Worker. Use notificationId as dedup key. Store sent notification IDs in a lightweight store (even in-memory with TTL, or a DB table). Providers like SendGrid also support client-supplied idempotency keys."
