      "risk": "Queue/DLQ not monitored — failed notifications sit unnoticed",
      "severity": "high",
      "mitigation": "Set up DLQ depth alarms from day one. CloudWatch alarm on SQS DLQ depth > 0 → Slack/PagerDuty. This is 15 minutes of configuration, not engineering work."
