      "risk": "Notification Router becomes a bottleneck or single point of failure",
      "severity": "medium",
      "mitigation": "Run multiple instances of the router behind the same queue (competing consumers). If the router crashes, messages stay in the queue and are processed when it recovers. Queue durability is the safety net."
